Feature: To Create an new account on Magento application

  Scenario: User has to create a new account on Magento application
    When To clicks on the Create an Account button
    And To enters valid First Name
    And To enters valid Last Name
    And To enters valid Email on email feild
    And To enters valid password on password feild
    And To enters valid Confirm Password on Confirm Password feild
    And To click the Create an Account button
